<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 03 at 9:55PM EST  by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>...Black Ice Tonight...
Melted snow and slush on untreated roads and sidewalks will freeze
tonight as temperatures bottom out in the single digits and teens.
Black ice will be difficult to see and may look like water on
surfaces. Use caution if traveling tonight and Tuesday morning.
Some roads will be slippery.</description>
